_entity_src_gen.pdbx_description                   
;Spinach nitrite reductase was produced as a His-tagged recombinant protein expressed from the pET30b-NiR plasmid in E. coli. The E. coli cells were co-transformed with the plasmid pKK233-CysG that contains the cysG gene encoding the enzyme that catalyzes the rate-limiting step in siroheme biosynthesis.
;
